title: T-Pain Interview and Dr.Sebi's family Interview
itunes:title: T-Pain Interview and Dr.Sebi's family Interview
description:
Today on the show we had T-Pain, the man that transitioned music to auto tune stop by where he spoke about having threesomes with his wife, going broke from 40 million, learning how to ignore the haters and be happy and more. Also we were honored to interview Dr.Sebi's family who is continuing his legacy by making products that heal the body
